rences between the solar extensions and stellar\nobservations at the wavelength in the 2-30 nm band and concluded that\nsimultaneous observations of magnetic and XUV/FUV fluxes are necessary for\nfurther validations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Feb 2023 00:31:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
