\ndual-comb oscillator provides a rapid yet highly precise optical delay sweep\nfrom a simple setup. Therefore, our approach will be beneficial for high-update\nrate time sampling and time-domain spectroscopy applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Feb 2023 08:53:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-22"}
