romising technique to\nidentify GRBs in the ACS data that can be implemented in the AGILE real-time\nanalysis pipeline.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Feb 2023 09:24:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-22"}
