pe-warps to demonstrate that negative energy\ndensity is not an intrinsic unavoidable feature of warp drives.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Feb 2023 23:54:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Apr 2023 17:20:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 20 Apr 2023 01:06:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-21"}
